; animated marker (24x12 pixels) is XOR-blitted on that room's deck
; map. Read by GetRoomMarkerAddr (#R35088), which feeds both marker
; channels: A — the walking crew figure (CrewWalkA1/A2) on the room
; being viewed, placed by PlaceRoomMarkerA (#R35101) — and B — the
; blinking box cursor (RoomCursor0-3) on a candidate room: an exit row
; under the cursor in the room view, or a room picked from the
