; AnimCrewAFrames
;
; 4 × 16-bit pointers to crew animation frame-A sprite bitmaps.
; Indexed by frame phase (0-3); phases 0-1 share one bitmap, 2-3 share
; another, producing a two-frame walk cycle at rate 10 (10 frames/step).
; Used by AnimateCrewA (#R34967) to XOR-blit crew sprites onto the screen.
;
@label=CrewWalkAnimA
