; Room adjacency map — corridor/door network
;
; The Nostromo's connectivity, as two 5-byte-per-room tables (this one and
; the air-duct network at #R29346). Room IDs 0-34 index the room-name table
; at #R28221. Each room has 5 direction slots holding the destination room
; reached by leaving in that direction; a slot equal to the room's own ID
; means "no exit that way". The graph is fully symmetric (every door works
; both ways).
; .
; A direction slot is chosen by ScriptNibbleToDirection (#R36763) from the
; ROM script stream, so AI wandering is a deterministic weighted random
; walk. Read by the destination picker at #R36717 (which writes an actor's
; record byte +2), by the alien's own per-move room step inside #R36859,
; and by the door-exit-list builder inside #R31634 that feeds the room
; view.
@label=RoomAdjCorridors
b29171 DEFB 13,13,0,0,0     ;  0 Airlock #1 -> 13 Corridor#6
 29176 DEFB 13,13,1,1,1     ;  1 Airlock #2 -> 13 Corridor#6
 29181 DEFB 10,10,10,2,2    ;  2 Armoury    -> 10 Corridor#3
 29186 DEFB 4,4,3,3,3       ;  3 Cargopod#1 -> 4 Cargopod#2
 29191 DEFB 32,3,14,5,9     ;  4 Cargopod#2 -> 3 Cargopod#1, 5 Cargopod#3, 9 Corridor#2, 14 Corridor#7, 32 ShuttleBay
 29196 DEFB 4,4,5,5,5       ;  5 Cargopod#3 -> 4 Cargopod#2
 29201 DEFB 8,8,8,6,6       ;  6 CommdCentr -> 8 Corridor#1
 29206 DEFB 13,13,30,30,7   ;  7 Computer   -> 13 Corridor#6, 30 Stores #2
 29211 DEFB 6,21,9,23,26    ;  8 Corridor#1 -> 6 CommdCentr, 9 Corridor#2, 21 Infirmary, 23 Laboratory, 26 Livng Qtrs
 29216 DEFB 8,4,10,15,12    ;  9 Corridor#2 -> 4 Cargopod#2, 8 Corridor#1, 10 Corridor#3, 12 Corridor#5, 15 Cryo Vault
 29221 DEFB 9,22,2,17,11    ; 10 Corridor#3 -> 2 Armoury, 9 Corridor#2, 11 Corridor#4, 17 Engine #1, 22 Inf Stores
 29226 DEFB 10,10,12,12,18  ; 11 Corridor#4 -> 10 Corridor#3, 12 Corridor#5, 18 Engine #2
 29231 DEFB 9,24,29,19,11   ; 12 Corridor#5 -> 9 Corridor#2, 11 Corridor#4, 19 Engine #3, 24 Lab Stores, 29 Stores #1
 29236 DEFB 27,0,7,31,1     ; 13 Corridor#6 -> 0 Airlock #1, 1 Airlock #2, 7 Computer, 27 Mess, 31 Stores #3
 29241 DEFB 4,4,25,25,14    ; 14 Corridor#7 -> 4 Cargopod#2, 25 Life Suppt
 29246 DEFB 9,9,15,15,15    ; 15 Cryo Vault -> 9 Corridor#2
 29251 DEFB 32,32,20,20,16  ; 16 Engineerng -> 20 Eng Stores, 32 ShuttleBay
 29256 DEFB 10,10,17,17,17  ; 17 Engine #1  -> 10 Corridor#3
 29261 DEFB 11,11,18,18,18  ; 18 Engine #2  -> 11 Corridor#4
 29266 DEFB 12,12,19,19,19  ; 19 Engine #3  -> 12 Corridor#5
 29271 DEFB 16,16,16,20,20  ; 20 Eng Stores -> 16 Engineerng
 29276 DEFB 8,8,8,21,21     ; 21 Infirmary  -> 8 Corridor#1
 29281 DEFB 10,10,10,22,22  ; 22 Inf Stores -> 10 Corridor#3
 29286 DEFB 8,8,8,23,23     ; 23 Laboratory -> 8 Corridor#1
 29291 DEFB 12,12,12,24,24  ; 24 Lab Stores -> 12 Corridor#5
 29296 DEFB 14,14,25,25,25  ; 25 Life Suppt -> 14 Corridor#7
 29301 DEFB 28,8,27,27,26   ; 26 Livng Qtrs -> 8 Corridor#1, 27 Mess, 28 RecrtnArea
 29306 DEFB 26,28,13,27,27  ; 27 Mess       -> 13 Corridor#6, 26 Livng Qtrs, 28 RecrtnArea
 29311 DEFB 26,26,27,27,28  ; 28 RecrtnArea -> 26 Livng Qtrs, 27 Mess
 29316 DEFB 12,12,12,29,29  ; 29 Stores #1  -> 12 Corridor#5
 29321 DEFB 7,7,30,30,30    ; 30 Stores #2  -> 7 Computer
 29326 DEFB 13,13,31,31,31  ; 31 Stores #3  -> 13 Corridor#6
 29331 DEFB 33,34,4,16,32   ; 32 ShuttleBay -> 4 Cargopod#2, 16 Engineerng, 33 Shttlstore, 34 Narcissus
