; Room adjacency map — air-duct network
;
; Companion table to #R29171 (RoomAdjCorridors): same 5-slot-per-room
; format, but describing the air-duct/crawlway network that connects the
; same rooms along different edges (e.g. Mess connects directly to both
; Airlocks, Computer to Engine #2). Only 34 entries — the Narcissus
; (room 34) cannot be reached through the ducts.
; .
; An actor whose record byte +1 has bit 6 set is travelling in this
; network; destinations fetched from here are stored with bit 6 set too,
; keeping the actor in duct space until a room handler clears the flag.
; Read by the duct branch of the destination picker at #R36717, by the
; grille-list builder inside #R31634 that lists a room's duct openings,
; and by the duct-entry move inside #R35382 that sends a crew member
; through a grille. The two one-way links (Airlock #2 -> Cargopod#1 and
; Stores #3 -> Airlock #2) are present in the original data.
@label=RoomAdjDucts
b29346 DEFB 0,30,27,26,0    ;  0 Airlock #1 -> 26 Livng Qtrs, 27 Mess, 30 Stores #2
 29351 DEFB 27,3,1,28,27    ;  1 Airlock #2 -> 3 Cargopod#1, 27 Mess, 28 RecrtnArea
 29356 DEFB 2,11,11,22,22   ;  2 Armoury    -> 11 Corridor#4, 22 Inf Stores
 29361 DEFB 33,14,14,3,3    ;  3 Cargopod#1 -> 14 Corridor#7, 33 Shttlstore
 29366 DEFB 4,14,14,14,4    ;  4 Cargopod#2 -> 14 Corridor#7
 29371 DEFB 5,14,20,20,5    ;  5 Cargopod#3 -> 14 Corridor#7, 20 Eng Stores
 29376 DEFB 6,8,8,6,6       ;  6 CommdCentr -> 8 Corridor#1
 29381 DEFB 7,18,18,13,13   ;  7 Computer   -> 13 Corridor#6, 18 Engine #2
 29386 DEFB 21,8,23,6,8     ;  8 Corridor#1 -> 6 CommdCentr, 21 Infirmary, 23 Laboratory
 29391 DEFB 10,10,12,12,9   ;  9 Corridor#2 -> 10 Corridor#3, 12 Corridor#5
 29396 DEFB 22,10,9,21,10   ; 10 Corridor#3 -> 9 Corridor#2, 21 Infirmary, 22 Inf Stores
 29401 DEFB 2,18,29,15,2    ; 11 Corridor#4 -> 2 Armoury, 15 Cryo Vault, 18 Engine #2, 29 Stores #1
 29406 DEFB 9,9,24,23,23    ; 12 Corridor#5 -> 9 Corridor#2, 23 Laboratory, 24 Lab Stores
 29411 DEFB 30,7,31,27,13   ; 13 Corridor#6 -> 7 Computer, 27 Mess, 30 Stores #2, 31 Stores #3
 29416 DEFB 3,25,5,4,14     ; 14 Corridor#7 -> 3 Cargopod#1, 4 Cargopod#2, 5 Cargopod#3, 25 Life Suppt
 29421 DEFB 15,11,11,15,15  ; 15 Cryo Vault -> 11 Corridor#4
 29426 DEFB 16,16,20,32,32  ; 16 Engineerng -> 20 Eng Stores, 32 ShuttleBay
 29431 DEFB 17,18,18,17,17  ; 17 Engine #1  -> 18 Engine #2
 29436 DEFB 17,7,19,11,25   ; 18 Engine #2  -> 7 Computer, 11 Corridor#4, 17 Engine #1, 19 Engine #3, 25 Life Suppt
 29441 DEFB 19,18,18,19,19  ; 19 Engine #3  -> 18 Engine #2
 29446 DEFB 16,5,5,20,20    ; 20 Eng Stores -> 5 Cargopod#3, 16 Engineerng
 29451 DEFB 21,10,8,8,21    ; 21 Infirmary  -> 8 Corridor#1, 10 Corridor#3
 29456 DEFB 2,10,10,22,22   ; 22 Inf Stores -> 2 Armoury, 10 Corridor#3
 29461 DEFB 8,12,12,23,23   ; 23 Laboratory -> 8 Corridor#1, 12 Corridor#5
 29466 DEFB 24,12,29,29,24  ; 24 Lab Stores -> 12 Corridor#5, 29 Stores #1
 29471 DEFB 25,25,14,18,18  ; 25 Life Suppt -> 14 Corridor#7, 18 Engine #2
 29476 DEFB 26,0,28,28,26   ; 26 Livng Qtrs -> 0 Airlock #1, 28 RecrtnArea
 29481 DEFB 0,13,1,27,27    ; 27 Mess       -> 0 Airlock #1, 1 Airlock #2, 13 Corridor#6
 29486 DEFB 26,1,1,28,28    ; 28 RecrtnArea -> 1 Airlock #2, 26 Livng Qtrs
 29491 DEFB 29,11,11,24,29  ; 29 Stores #1  -> 11 Corridor#4, 24 Lab Stores
