; RoomDispatchTable
@ignoreua
;
; Word table with a clever triple use. The action key (HandleInput at
; $881B) dispatches table[room_mode] with room_mode from #R31252:
;    0-1  RoomModeDispatch   (#R35314)
;    2-3  LocationListAction (#R35338) — Indicate Location list,
;         pages 1 (rooms 0-16) and 2 (rooms 17-33)
;    4    GetItemPick        (#R35578) — item picked from the Get strip
; For modes 0 and 1 RoomModeDispatch then re-dispatches on the cursor
; ROW through overlapping halves of this same table (entry 5 onward =
; base $840C, entry 23 onward = base $8430):
; .
; Mode-0 rows (orders screen), base $840C:
;    0     "Order:" header       -> RoomHandlerNop (#R35448)
;    1-7   crew slots 1-7        -> OpenCrewRoomView (#R35163)
;    8     " Indicate "          -> IndicateLocation (#R35222): opens
;                                   the room-location list (mode 2)
;    9     " Location "          -> nop (2nd row of the 2-row label)
;    10-11 " Display  "/"  Level"-> nop (header for the deck rows)
;    12-14 Upper/Middle/Lower    -> SelectDeckMap (#R35210): deck map
;    15-18 blank                 -> nop
; .
; Mode-1 rows (room view / action menu), base $8430:
;    0     "move to:" header     -> nop
;    1     "Grille" (open duct)  -> MoveThroughGrille (#R35560)
;    2-6   exit rooms            -> MoveToRoom (#R35382)
;    7     " use:" header        -> nop
;    8     front-hand item       -> RoomHandlerNop2 (#R35449); but the
;                                   pre-dispatch hook ($B2C0) zeroes the
;                                   actor's action countdown — pressing
;                                   the held-item row cancels a pending
;                                   timed job
;    9     back-hand item        -> SwapHeldItems (#R35451)
;    10    "Get Item"            -> GetItemMenu (#R35638)
;    11    "Leave Item"          -> LeaveItemHandler (#R35725)
;    12    "Special" header      -> nop
;    13    special action        -> $8BCB -> SpecialRowAction ($B306):
;                                   52 ATTACK / 49 RmveGrille / 238 =
;                                   RmveGrille swapped to ATTACK under
;                                   the cursor (hostile in the room —
;                                   see PreDispatchHook $B2B9)
;    14    "Get Jones"           -> GetJonesHandler (#R35845):
;                                   needs the Net or the Cat Box
;    15-16 fixture actions       -> FixtureAction (#R38398)
;    17    "   QUIT   "          -> QuitRoomView (#R35440)
;    18    blank                 -> nop (reuses CrewActionDispatch+0)
; .
; The mode-1 row words for rows 11-17 are the "RoomDispatchTailExtra"
; bytes at #R33862; row 18 overlaps CrewActionDispatch's first entry.
@ignoreua
@label=RoomDispatchTable
w33794 DEFW 35314,35314,35338,35338
 33802 DEFW 35578,35448,35163,35163
 33810 DEFW 35163,35163,35163,35163
 33818 DEFW 35163,35222,35448,35448
 33826 DEFW 35448,35210,35210,35210
 33834 DEFW 35448,35448,35448,35448
 33842 DEFW 35560,35382,35382,35382
 33850 DEFW 35382,35382,35448,35449
 33858 DEFW 35451,35638

; Dispatch-table tails and message text
;
; Three back-to-back data tables (once misclassified as a code routine,
; "GetCorridorTableEntry"):
; .
;   #R33862 (14 bytes, 7 × 16-bit pointers) — RoomDispatchTailExtra, the
;       tail of the RoomDispatchTable at #R33794: the mode-1 row words for
;       rows 11-17 (see that table's header), sharing the same small
;       handler pool.
;   #R33876 (16 bytes, 8 × 16-bit pointers) — CrewActionDispatch,
;       indexed by crew/alien action state in (IX+3). Action 0 returns
;       early; actions 1-7 jump to the matching handler. Used by the
;       routine at #R36014.
;   #R33892 (744 bytes) — MessageTextTable, 34 strings terminated
;       by byte 255. Substitution codes inside the strings: 254 = actor
;       name, 253 = target name, 252 = room name, 145 = apostrophe glyph.
;       Walked and rendered by the routine at #R37221.
; .
;       Triggers (message # -> firing condition):
;         0  Jones enters a living crew member's room (#R36859)
;         1  alien attack tick, victim strength still >= 4
;         2  Get Jones action succeeds (JonesRoom := 255 = carried)
;         3/4  crew nets / hits the alien (CrewHitsAlien outcomes)
;         5/6/7  weapon spent: Tracker / extinguisher (also fire handler
;                with no charges) / Laser
;         8  room damage event, cell value 55
;         9  fire breaks out in a room
;         10 alien attack tick, victim strength 2-3
;         11/12 hypersleep pod entered (#R38529) / completed (#R38784)
;         13/14 destruct lever armed / aborted (DestructArm/DestructAbort)
;         15 engine-room fire fully extinguished
;         16/17 airlock blown (BlowLock) / resealed (SealLock)
;         18 alien re-enters via ShuttleBay after surviving an airlock
;            blow
;         19 actor stands beside Jones's strip cells 20/21
;         20 actor shares a room with a dead crew member
;         21 victim strength exhausted - collapse
;         22/23/24/25 accumulated room damage crosses the '3x' threshold
;            in CommdCentr / Computer / Life Suppt / Narcissus (AddRoomDamage
;            #R38186, damage digits at #R30006)
;         26 oxygen clock reaches "05:00"
;         27/28 launch check: Jones missing / crew not all aboard
;            (LaunchGate #R40212)
;         29/30/31/32 Android combat set (UpdateAlien / CrewHitsAndroid)
;         33 Long Game opening: chestburster host named (LongGameInit)
@ignoreua
@label=RoomDispatchTailExtra
b33862 DEFW 35725,35448  ; rows 11-12
 33866 DEFW 35787,35845  ; rows 13-14
 33870 DEFW 38398,38398,35440 ; rows 15-17
@label=CrewActionDispatch
 33876 DEFW 35448,36034
 33880 DEFW 36101,36150
 33884 DEFW 37520,39256
 33888 DEFW 38784,40757
@label=MessageTextTable
