 37619 JP NC,37555   ; also useless
 37622 CP 16         ; the Net?
 37624 JR NZ,37646   ; no → "hits the ALIEN" branch
@ignoreua
 37626 LD HL,29566   ; yes: stamp 255 into the alien's countdown
@ignoreua
