 39255 RET           ;

; CrewAction5_AlienAttack — the alien's attack tick (action state 5)
;
; Dispatched via CrewActionDispatch entry 5, queued by UpdateAlienAI
; (#R37018) when crew share the alien's spot. Re-gathers the crew on
; the alien's spot (up to three into NearestCrewC/A/B), picks one by
; script roll, and drains a strength point: below 2 the victim
; collapses (VictimItemDrop #R39400, msg #21), at 2-3 msg #10 "is
; being wounded", and a still-fit victim (4+) gets msg #1 "The ALIEN
; is attacking {actor}". A chosen victim who is already dead may be
; dragged off the ship (Wound_PanicRoll, in the #R39400 block), else
; another gathered slot is tried; with nobody left the alien moves
; on.
