; Arms the alien body animation (sets freeze flag so a single blit occurs next frame),
; or ends the encounter sequence. If (RoomModeByte)=1 the crew member was killed: jump to
; #R32719 to handle that. Otherwise clears the screen area and returns.
; This entry point is used by the routines at #R36793 and #R37992.
