; AdvanceJonesPos
;
; Increments JonesPos by 4. If the new value >= 136 the tail sweep is complete:
; freeze the Y animation (JonesPhase |= 128) and return. Otherwise store the new
; position, cycle the phase counter (0->1->2->3->4->0) and jump back to BlitJonesFrame.
