; TriggerAlienEvent — arm the Android once the alien is hurt
;
; Per-frame check: once the crew has wounded the alien 6 or more
; times (slot 0 byte +4), and a valid Android slot exists
; (AlienTargetID < 8 — Long Game only) whose record is still dormant
; (+7 = 0), set AlienActiveFlag = 255 via AlienEventDispatch
; (#R45732). UpdateAlien (#R40826) sees the flag and turns the
; Android hostile — the traitor reveals himself when the alien is in
; danger.
; .
; Used by the routine at #R36457.
