; IntroductionMode
;
; Game-mode handler for "3: Introduction" (dispatched from #R43135):
; the "MAPPING SYMBOLS" legend page. On a black screen it prints the
; map-symbol legend (connecting door, ladder, hatchway, grille), stamps
; the two animated map markers next to their captions (channel A's
; walking crew figure = "Subject Indicator", channel B's blinking box
; = "Room Indicator"), then demos three sound effects with captions
; ("This is the sound of a" Door being opened / Grille being removed /
; Positive Tracker Reading), animating the markers throughout. Waits
